{"id":52013,"date":"2021-03-27T11:08:13","date_gmt":"2021-03-27T10:08:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=52013"},"modified":"2021-03-27T11:08:22","modified_gmt":"2021-03-27T10:08:22","slug":"travel-safety","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/","title":{"rendered":"Travel Safety: 17 Tips on How to Travel Safe"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-1-spend-money-to-travel-safe\">1. Spend Money to Travel Safe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you arriving late at night in a new country? You might be trying to travel on a budget, but nothing is more valuable than your travel safety. Spend money on a taxi, or stay in an airport hotel to travel safely.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Travel Safety Tip:<\/strong> Traveling to a country that is known for being a little unsafe? It&#x2019;s well worth spending the money on joining an organized tour group. Not only will they plan everything for you, but it&#x2019;s also much safer, and the tour guides have valuable inside knowledge.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081542\/travel-safety-tips-bangkok.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety tips bangkok\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safety tips bangkok\" class=\"w