-safe-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081459\/how-to-travel-safe-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-3-dress-smart-for-your-travel-safety\">3. Dress smart for your travel safety<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Think of the classic tourist, someone walking around with their head in a map or phone and a camera around their neck. Standing out like this can make you a target for thieves and scams. However, there are a few top tips to keep help you travel safe:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Know where you&#x2019;re going beforehand<\/strong> so you don&#x2019;t have to get your map out. The same goes for travel in between your transport to your destination. If you arrive off the train and don&#x2019;t know where you&#x2019;re going, it&#x2019;ll be immediately obvious.<\/li><li><strong>Walk with confidence<\/strong>. This makes you look like a local or at least someone who knows the area.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety streets\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safety streets\" data-id=\"54535\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=54535\" class=\"wp-image-54535 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-streets-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081517\/travel-safety-street