                 <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Travel Safety Tip:<\/strong> Alert your bank or telephone provider if your phone or credit cards are stolen to prevent receiving a huge bill.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety outfit\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safety outfit\" class=\"wp-image-54533 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081521\/travel-safety-outfit.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-4-buy-travel-insurance\">4. Buy Travel Insurance<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important parts of travel safe is getting <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">travel insurance<\/a>! This protects you against all unforeseen costs, whether it&#x2019;s a hospital visit, stolen belongings, or a missed flight. It&#x2019;s very unlikely you&#x2019;ll have to use it, but it&#x2019;s an important part of safe travel. During our 5 years of traveling, we did had to use it multiple times for hospital visits and it&#x2019;s good to mention that due to your travel insurance you can go to an international hospital instead of the local one where the care is often much better. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Best Travel Insurances<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19.jpg\" alt=\"best travel insurance covid 19\"><\/noscript><img width=\"366\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best travel insurance covid 19\" class=\"wp-image-34605 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-300x277.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-600x553.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-650x600.jpg 650w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-878x810.jpg 878w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-366x338.jpg 366w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-1536x1417.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-30x28.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113930\/best-travel-insurance-covid-19-163x150.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/231