lar places. <\/strong>Is there a line? Good! <\/li><li><strong>Make sure your water is clean<\/strong>. A water purifier is a great way to purify your water and avoid single-use plastic. Read more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">traveling plastic-free<\/a>.<\/li><li><strong>Avoid ice and salads<\/strong>. Both are usually washed or made with tap water.<\/li><li><strong>Eat peel-able fruit. <\/strong>Avoid bacteria by only eating fruit that you have to peel yourself.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food-577x810.jpg\" alt=\"travel safe street food\"><\/noscript><img width=\"241\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safe street food\" data-id=\"54542\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=54542\" class=\"wp-image-54542 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food-577x810.jpg 577w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food-428x600.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food-241x338.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\/travel-safe-street-food-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081509\