lock-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety taxi\"><\/noscript><img width=\"439\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safety taxi\" class=\"wp-image-54519 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1720px) 100vw, 1720px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi.jpg 1720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-779x600.jpg 779w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-1052x810.jpg 1052w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-439x338.jpg 439w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-163x125.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-234x180.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-768x591.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-1024x788.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-1403x1080.jpg 1403w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-300x231.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-600x462.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081548\/travel-safety-taxi.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-7-know-the-areas-to-avoid-for-your-travel-safety\">7. Know the Areas to Avoid for your Travel Safety<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most fun parts of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-plan-trip\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">planning a trip<\/a> is doing the research! Whilst you&#x2019;re doing this, check your government travel advice, and they will explain what to look out for. For example, malaria warnings, natural disasters, or safety advice for certain cities or regions. Your local government&#x2019;s page will also be regularly updated if anything changes. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Good to know:<\/strong> Government advice is there to warn you of the worst-case scenario. You&#x2019;ll most likely have an amazing trip, so don&#x2019;t let it scare you.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081451\/safety-traveling-tips.jpg\" alt=\"dogs beach asia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"419\" height=\"338\" alt=\"dogs beach asia\" class=\"wp-image-54577 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081451\/safety-traveling-tips.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081451\/safety-traveling-tips-745x600.jpg 745w, https:\/\/static.salti