h3 id=\"h-free-travel-safety-tips\">Free Travel Safety tips<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Browse Facebook pages and traveler forums to find out information about the particular area you&#x2019;re visiting. Other travelers have invaluable insight into the things to look out for. Additionally, ask the staff at your accommodation which neighborhoods to avoid. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Here&#x2019;s:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-plan-trip\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to plan a trip (7 easy tips!)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081448\/how-to-travel-safe-facebook-group.jpg\" alt=\"how to travel safe facebook group\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"how to travel safe facebook group\" class=\"wp-image-54580 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081448\/how-to-travel-safe-facebook-group.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081448\/how-to-travel-safe-facebook-group-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081448\/how-to-travel-safe-facebook-group-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081448\/how-to-travel-safe-facebook-group-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\