heck no one is watching you. If you feel uneasy, move on to the next ATM. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of ATM fees, it&#x2019;s often tempting to take out cash in large amounts. However, avoid doing this by taking out small amounts and using a travel cash card that waves the fees. This way, if it gets stolen, it won&#x2019;t be such a big deal.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Budget tip:<\/strong> Avoid ATM fees by using a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wise Travel Money Card. (Formerly Transferwise)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081527\/travel-safety-money-card-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety money card\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"travel safety money card\" class=\"wp-image-54531 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081527\/travel-safety-money-card-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081527\/travel-safety-money-card-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081527\/travel-safety-money-card-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081527\/travel-safety-money-card-30x20.jpg 