ip: you could use it as a pillow on long trips.&#xA0;Win-win!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-lock-your-bags-for-the-best-travel-safety\">Lock your bags for the best travel safety<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Padlocking your bags is also a great deterrent for thieves. However, make sure the material cant be slashed or easily ripped. There are loads of great backpacks on the market made of anti-theft material like these <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/pacsafe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Pacsafe Bags<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Padlocks are also great to use for your locker at your accommodation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco.jpg\" alt=\"rugs morocco\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"rugs morocco\" class=\"wp-image-54598 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081423\/travel-safety-morocco-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/