          <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-11-share-your-route-with-your-family-and-friends\">11. Share Your Route With Your Family and Friends<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One easy way to travel safely is to keep your family or friends updated with your route. This is particularly important if you&#x2019;re going somewhere without wifi or phone signal so that they don&#x2019;t get worried.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An extra option would be to turn on your &#x2018;Find My Phone&#x2019; feature. This way they can track where you are, or you can find your phone when it is lost or stolen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact.jpg\" alt=\"how to travel safe contact\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"324\" alt=\"how to travel safe contact\" class=\"wp-image-54596 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact-800x577.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact-1080x779.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact-450x324.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact-163x117.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081427\/how-to-travel-safe-contact-250x180.jpg 250w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.