alt=\"safe accommodation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"safe accommodation\" class=\"wp-image-54591 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-600x776.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081430\/travel-safety-accommodation.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The same goes when booking taxis. One well-known scam is where a taxi collects you from your accommodation and later returns to steal your belongings. Instead, tell the taxi to pick you up from a busy, well-lit location close to where you&#x2019;re staying. Additionally, if you&#x2019;ve pre-booked a taxi, wait for them to clarify your name so you know this is definitely your taxi and not a scam. Also, by using a taxi application like Uber or Grab you will see trustworthy reviews of the driver. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081438\/streets-thailand-547x810.jpg\" alt=\"streets thailand\"><\/noscript><img width=\"228\" height=\"338\" alt=\"streets thailand\" data-id=\"54586\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081438\/streets-thailand.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=54586\" class=\"wp-image-54586 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081438\/streets-thailand-547x810.jpg 547w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081438\/streets-thailand-405x600.jpg 405w, https:\/