81434\/travel-safety-tips-taxi.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081434\/travel-safety-tips-taxi-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081434\/travel-safety-tips-taxi-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-13-avoid-unnecessary-danger\">13. Avoid Unnecessary Danger<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s easy to get caught up in the whirlwind of travel, adopting an adventurous attitude that can lead you to take unnecessary risks. For example, leaving the path to get to a secret spot or riding on a motorbike with no helmet. Personally, we take risks to get a photo at a cliff, but we&#x2019;re always careful and wouldn&#x2019;t do it if it were too sketchy. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety watersports\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safety watersports\" class=\"wp-image-54583 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081444\/travel-safety-watersports.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-14-travel-safety-being-able-to-save-yourself-and-others\">14. Travel Safety: Being able to save yourself and others<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before you leave, consider taking a first-aid course, or a language course to teach you how to ask for help. Especially for women traveling alone, a self-defense class can be invaluable. Hopefully, you&#x2019;ll never have to use what you&#x2019;ve learned but it can give you the confidence to travel solo and safely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language.jpg\" alt=\"travel safe learn language\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"travel safe learn language\" class=\"wp-image-54524 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081538\/travel-safe-learn-language.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-15-travel-safe-in-a-group\">15. Travel Safe in a Group<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Traveling solo is wonderful; however, traveling in a group means that you have extra pairs of eyes and ears to stay safe while traveling. Whether you meet people in your hostel or travel via an organized tour, it&#x2019;s a great way to make friends and look after each other. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, even if you are traveling solo, travel safety always comes down to trusting your instinct, relax and enjoy the journey. Just remember that what seems unsafe normally is.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group.jpg\" alt=\"travel group\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"331\" alt=\"travel group\" class=\"wp-image-54538 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-800x588.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-1080x794.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-450x331.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-163x120.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-245x180.jpg 245w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-768x565.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-1024x753.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-1440x1059.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-300x221.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-600x441.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081513\/travel-group.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-16-register-with-your-embassy\">16. Register With Your Embassy<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>By registering with your embassy, they&#x2019;ll keep you up to date on warnings and advice, helping you to travel safely. This means that if a natural disaster occurs or a pandemic, they can help to return you home.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Good to know: <\/strong>Having your embassy within easy contact is also great if you lose or damage your passport, as they can sort this quickly.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081404\/tips-travel-safety.jpg\" alt=\"tips travel safety\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tips travel safety\" class=\"wp-image-54610 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081404\/tips-travel-safety.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081404\/tips-travel-safety-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081404\/tips-travel-safety-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081404\/tips-travel-safety-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.