s, and make you less aware of potential danger.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sadly, there are reports of people having &#x2018;date rape&#x2019; drugs slipped into their drink while partying. To prevent this, never leave your drink unattended, keep your hand over your drink, or purchase a drink cover.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Remember:<\/strong> Drinks can be much stronger in different countries. As a result, you might be able to drink 4 beers at home, but it doesn&#x2019;t mean you&#x2019;ll be able to abroad. Add to that altitude or heatstroke, and your tolerance to alcohol can be really affected.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party.jpg\" alt=\"travel safety party\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel safety party\" class=\"wp-image-54550 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/28081455\/travel-safety-party-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/up